---
// Hero section - simplified
---

<section class="hero section section--dark" id="top">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="hero__content">
      <h1 class="hero__title">Allt om indexfonder</h1>

      <p class="hero__subtitle">
        Lär dig hur indexfonder fungerar, vilka som presterar bäst, och hur du kommer igång med ditt sparande.
        En komplett guide från Opti.
      </p>

      <div class="hero__cta-group">
        <a href="#vad-ar-indexfond" class="btn btn--primary btn--large">
          Läs guiden
          <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
            <path d="M12 5v14M19 12l-7 7-7-7"/>
          </svg>
        </a>
        <a href="https://opti.se" class="btn btn--outline btn--large" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
          Prova Opti
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="hero__bg-gradient"></div>
</section>

<style>
  .hero {
    min-height: 100vh;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
    padding-top: 72px;
  }

  .hero__content {
    max-width: 800px;
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
  }

  .hero__title {
    font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 6vw, 4rem);
    font-weight: 700;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    line-height: 1.1;
  }

  .hero__subtitle {
    font-size: var(--font-size-xl);
    color: var(--gray-300);
    margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
    max-width: 600px;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .hero__cta-group {
    display: flex;
    gap: 1rem;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }

  .hero__bg-gradient {
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    right: -20%;
    width: 80%;
    height: 100%;
    background: radial-gradient(ellipse at center, rgba(62, 205, 163, 0.15) 0%, transparent 70%);
    pointer-events: none;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .hero {
      min-height: auto;
      padding-top: calc(72px + 3rem);
      padding-bottom: 3rem;
    }

    .hero__cta-group {
      flex-direction: column;
    }
  }
</style>
